Name: Exterran Partners, L.P.
Description: Exterran Partners, L.P. provides natural gas contract operations services to customers throughout the United States. The Company engaged in acquiring certain contract operations customer service agreements and a compressor fleet used to provide compression services under those agreements. Exterran General Partner, L.P., its general partner, is an indirect, wholly owned subsidiary of Exterran Holdings, Inc. (Exterran Holdings). Exterran GP LLC, is the general partner of Exterran General Partner, L.P., which conducts the Company's business and operations. As of December 31, 2011, Exterran Holdings owned 35% interest in the Company. In April 2013, the Company has completed the acquisition of compression assets from Exterran Holdings.
